data.description:
Welcome to this lovely well maintained 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home in the highly desired LPGA International Golf Course Community of Daytona Beach.As you enter the home you will notice the natural light flooding the open concept kitchen and family room.  With sliding doors to the enclosed patio, enjoy the Florida falls with the Waterview's and no rear neighbors. 
 Roof was replaced in 2019 and the AC was updated with a new compressor and defroster board.   This is a move in ready home ready to show!  Schedule your showing today!
